data.description: If you are looking for space for everyone with a relaxing & unique water view, come take a look! This 4 bedroom, 3 full bathroom, one owner, Simmons home, is situated in a quiet cul-de-sac with a beautiful pond view. An open concept floor plan is thoughtfully curated with a well designed kitchen that includes a gas stove, island with stainless steel sink, large pantry and an abundance of granite countertop space. The dining room sits just off the kitchen, is open to the living room and has incredible views of the pond through large sliding glass doors. Tall ceilings in the main living area add to the overall feeling of spaciousness that offers plenty of room for large furniture pieces. Just across the hallway from the laundry room, the primary bedroom has the ultimate morning sunrise views overlooking the pond, a primary suite with double sinks, shower, soaking tub and massive primary closet. 3 additional bedrooms, with nice sized closets and 2 full bathrooms, share the opposite side of the house. Take a load off and relax in your quiet backyard overlooking a peaceful pond. This highly desirable community is conveniently located less than 2 miles from Highways 75 and 67. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful home your own. Schedule your private showing today!
